des:
Calex Smart products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. 

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you light- just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Calex Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Calex Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2) Register one account in our "Calex Smart" app;
(3) You need to have some Calex Smart devices in hand;
(4) Configure these devices in our “Calex Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Calex Smart" skill;
(5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7) Search "Calex Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of "Calex Smart", and you'll be navigated to Calex Smart login page;
(9) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10) Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the light.
Alexa, turn off the plug.
Alexa, set the light to 50%.
Alexa, brighten the light to 50%.
Alexa, dim the light to 50%.
Alexa, set the light to green.
